com.unvired.model
Class InfoMessage

java.lang.Object
  com.unvired.model.DataStructure
      com.unvired.model.InfoMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataStructure
public class InfoMessage
extends DataStructure

Server sends info, success, error and warning messages to the mobile device as InfoMessages. The info message has to be interpreted as follows:

  • getCategory() - Provides the category of the message - info, success, warning or failure.
  • getMessage() - Provides the message text.
  • getBeName() - Provides the name of the business entity associated with the message.
  • getBeLid() - Provides the local identifier of the business entity associated with the message.
  • getMessageBlob() - Provides detailed message as bytes.
